dict.string: Sir Topham Hatt was very pleased with Thomas. “You made the right decision to pull Diesel back. You didn’t wait to be asked or to be told.” As a reward, Thomas would visit the Mainland and bring back more jobi wood. The next day, while Thomas waited to be loaded onto a ship, Salty told him and Percy about Misty Island. “It’s a mysterious place,” Salty huffed. “Once an engine was lost there and couldn’t be found because of the mist.” “If I were lost on Misty Island,” Thomas peeped, “I’d puff three times.” “I’d come save you,” Percy promised.
